column3: I've been talking to |murder.killer.job.employer.owner.fullname|, and they have had it with your wanton theft of our IP! I'm warning you to knock it off, or else...
If I see you around |murder.killer.job.employer.location.street| again... Let's not get into it, shall we?
We all make choices, but some decisions have a way of catching up with us, don’t they? You’ve been walking a fine line, and I’ve been patient. Too patient...
